title: Executive Order 11549-Revoking Executive Order No. 10361 of June 11, 1952, Establishing the Whittier Defensive Sea Area, Alaska
content: By virtue of the authority vested in me by Section 2152 of Title 18, United States Code, and as President of the United States, Executive Order No. 10361 of June 11, 1952, establishing the Whittier Defensive Sea Area, Alaska, is hereby revoked.
citation: Richard Nixon, Executive Order 11549-Revoking Executive Order No. 10361 of June 11, 1952, Establishing the Whittier Defensive Sea Area, Alaska Online by Gerhard Peters and John T. Woolley, The American Presidency Project https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/node/306563
